      "title": "Energy Minister in talks with Qatari officials",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka\u2019s Minister of Power & Energy Kanchana Wijesekara has called on Saad Sherida Al-Kaabi, the Minister of State for Energy Affairs, the President and CEO of Qatar Energy, to discuss the supply of Petroleum Products, LPG and LNG to the island nation to overcome the Energy crisis with the assistance of Qatar Energy and The Qatar Development Fund."
